Bundled third-party content:
- Azkar, Qur'an, and Asmaul Husna text/translations, and azan recordings:
  content assets from the IOM Daily Azkar project, used with permission.
- Fonts (Amiri, Scheherazade New, Noto Serif Bengali, Hind Siliguri, etc.):
  each under its own open-source license (SIL Open Font License / Apache),
  see assets/fonts/ for individual font licenses.
- SolaimanLipi and Al Majeed Quranic Font (AlQalam): widely-distributed
  freeware fonts commonly used in Bangla/Quranic software; bundled here
  under the same terms they're freely distributed under. Their exact
  redistribution license was not independently re-verified for this
  project -- worth double-checking before wide public distribution.
